soap.local.entity

Class Person

  • soap.local.entity.SOAPBaseType
    • soap.local.entity.GWObject
      • soap.local.entity.Contact
        • soap.local.entity.Person
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PersonVendor, UserContact

    public class Person
extends Contact
    Represents a person as a primary subtype of Contact.

    Person extends Contact with additional information about individuals that is not applicable to companies or places.
